An Act relating to abortion; creating the Abolition
10 of Abortion Act; stating purpose; specifying
applicability and construction of certain provisions;
11 making enforcement of certain violations subject to
specified factors; amending 12 O.S. 2021, Section
12 1053, which relates to wrongful death; modifying
applicability of certain provisions; amending 21 O.S.
13 2021, Section 691, which relates to homicide;
removing exceptions; prohibiting retroactivity;
14 providing for noncodification; providing for
